          "Rare inherited condition output is educational boundary context only and avoids diagnosis, disease-risk estimates, variant classification, carrier-status calls, inheritance inference, family-member risk, cascade testing, screening, treatment, procedure, medication, reproductive action, and clinical actionability claims.",
