                observedValue:
                  "validated dysautonomia model, autonomic testing, tilt-table testing, heart rate, blood pressure, syncope history, symptom history, medication context, hydration and salt context, neurologic or cardiology review, and clinical diagnosis unavailable in this fixture; sanitized official completed-output row structure observed separately with private values redacted",
