          hasBloodTraitsSample
            ? "Sample blood-trait, blood-type, cholesterol, glucose, inflammatory, iron, and clotting labels are used only as observed output structure; local output does not provide personal lab values, diagnosis, compatibility, medication, supplement, diet, testing, treatment, or actionability guidance."
            : hasDysautonomiaOfficialOutputCapture
